      • createSetOfUnitsForMerge

        public static RatesDTO createSetOfUnitsForMerge(java.math.BigDecimal amount,
                                java.util.Calendar rawRate,
                                Currency currency)
        pseudo-constructor for passing a set of units to merge. Returned instance contains the amount, the raw rate as Calendar (in field generalRawRate), and the currency.
        Parameters:
        amount - the amount of the set of units.
        rawRate - the raw rate as Calendar belonging to this set of units.
        currency - the currency of the amount.
        Returns:
        an instance of RatesDTO containing all necessary data.
